                  , spinster, on the King's highway, on the <rs id="t17850406-67-cd323" type="crimeDate">22d of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850406-67-off322 t17850406-67-cd323"></join> last, and putting her in fear and danger of her life, and feloniously taking from her person and against her will, one cloth cloak, value 2 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17850406-67-victim774" type="victimName">
                     Elizabeth 
                     Webb
                  <interp inst="t17850406-67-victim774" type="surname" value="Webb"></interp>
